## Architecture

Monorepo with MVVM across all platforms. API-first: OpenAPI spec drives typed clients.

```
{% if "backend" in platforms %}backend/       -> Spring Boot 4 (Kotlin 2.2+, Java 21) - Azure Container Apps{% endif %}
{% if "web-user-app" in platforms %}web-user-app/  -> Next.js + TypeScript user-facing web app - Cloudflare via OpenNext{% endif %}
{% if "web-admin-portal" in platforms %}web-admin-portal/  -> Next.js + TypeScript admin web portal - Cloudflare via OpenNext{% endif %}
{% if "mobile-android" in platforms %}mobile-android/       -> Kotlin + Jetpack Compose (MVVM, Hilt, Room){% endif %}
{% if "mobile-ios" in platforms %}mobile-ios/           -> Swift 6 + SwiftUI (MVVM, SwiftData) - Mac/Xcode only{% endif %}
shared/        -> OpenAPI spec + design tokens
docs/          -> Project-wide documentation (features, API, advisory board, deployment)
```

