## Conventions

- **API-first**: Define endpoints in OpenAPI -> generate clients -> implement
- **MVVM**: ViewModel + UiState/ViewState on both Android and iOS
- **DI**: Hilt (Android), protocol-based container (iOS), Spring (backend)
- **Tests**: MockK + Turbine (Android), XCTest (iOS), JUnit Jupiter 6 (backend)
- **Feature docs include Board Review** from virtual advisory board
- **One ViewModel per screen**, concrete repositories (no interface + impl boilerplate)

