## Adding Features

1. Define feature in `docs/features/` (use template from `docs/features/_template.md`)
2. Run advisory board review for strategic feedback
3. Add endpoints to `shared/api-contracts/openapi.yml`
4. Run `task generate-clients` to regenerate typed clients
5. Implement the selected platform slices that the feature actually touches. Backend usually leads when API or contract work is involved.
6. Update feature doc with implementation status

## Adding Endpoints

1. Add path + schemas to `shared/api-contracts/openapi.yml`
2. Run `task generate-clients`
3. Implement controller + service + repository in backend
4. Follow conventions in `docs/api/conventions.md`
